Transformations covered
1.Deduplication
Remove duplicate trip IDs introduced by upstream retries.
2.Null handling & imputation
Fill missing passenger counts, infer borough from GPS.
3.Type casting & parsing
Unify date formats across CSV/Parquet sources (schema drift).
4.Filtering & outlier removal
Drop trips with negative fares, zero distance, or 200+ mph speeds.
5.Joins (multi-source)
Enrich trips with zone names, weather conditions, and holiday flags.
6.Aggregations & window functions
Rolling 7-day revenue, hourly demand by zone, peak-hour ranking.
7.Slowly Changing Dimensions
Track zone boundary changes (SCD Type 2) over time.
8.Geospatial transforms
Haversine distance validation; zone polygon point-in-polygon check.
9.Pivot / unpivot
Wide-to-long payment breakdown (cash, card, no charge).
10.Derived columns
Tip %, speed (mph), time-of-day bucket, day-of-week label.
11.Incremental / CDC loading
Process only new months via watermark or Hudi/Delta merge.
12.ML feature engineering
Lag features, rolling averages for surge-price prediction model.

Suggested tech stack

Orchestration
Apache Airflow or Prefect for DAG-based scheduling.

Processing
PySpark / Spark SQL on EMR, Databricks, or local cluster.

Storage
S3/GCS in Parquet (Delta Lake or Apache Hudi for ACID).

Transformation
dbt for Silver→Gold SQL transformations with tests.

Warehouse
Snowflake, BigQuery, or DuckDB for analytical queries.

Visualization
Metabase, Grafana, or Superset for dashboards.
